{"tid":695681,"cid":7,"subCid":0,"title":"［犯賤］消瘦陳自瑤現身回應否認婚變。。。","createTime":"2018-06-09T11:50:45.000Z","updateTime":"2018-07-20T13:58:29.000Z","uid":56716,"like":11,"dislike":148,"uniUserReply":70,"replies":[{"pid":"c67cebd3f6a9b674fa6adcd25cb7ad29afb1e8c0","tid":695681,"uid":56716,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-09T11:50:45.000Z","msg":"對於婚變傳聞，陳自瑤同王浩信口徑一致，以三點作出回應，包括：<br />\n1.冇向王浩信提出離婚<br />\n2.亦冇趕老公出家門<br />\n3.囡囡仍同佢兩公婆一齊，並非傳聞指囡囡交由嫲嫲照顧。<br />\n<br />\n訪問期間，陳自瑤講咗五次或以上稱「近日所有報道係失實」，但扔拒用「恩愛」形容夫妻關係，只係話「老夫老妻」，又指對上一次對方做令佢感動嘅事係上年八月生日。陳自瑤又否認消瘦，話係著衫技巧，又澄清一向都冇戴婚戒嘅習慣。<br />\n<br />\n至於ig上嘅感性文字，陳自瑤表示只係有感而發，並非暗示夫妻關係有變，又指傳媒斷章取義，未有顧及前文後理。講到話少放兩公婆合照，陳稱一向都少，更反問係咪如果佢少咗擺同女兒合照，是否就代表母女關係有問題呢？<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.entertainment.appledaily.com/enews/realtime/article/20180609/58297546\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.entertainment.appledaily.com%2Fenews%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20180609%2F58297546&d=pmnSWfWqNx0i5qNhJfQyaP1gJfeR7%2BEkjjir5NquRfg%3D&h=3c73d3fb\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.entertainment.appledaily.com%2Fenews%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20180609%2F58297546&h=d54bf7f3\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.entertainment.appledaily.com/enews/realtime/article/20180609/58297546</a><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">個樣成個苦瓜乾咁，皮笑肉不笑，眼神似怨婦，好心yoyo咪咁犯賤啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> </span>"},{"pid":"fa82f30975d271bfa818b0dc56d3e77b83090af2","tid":695681,"uid":78622,"like":78,"dislike":64,"score":14,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-06-09T11:51:27.000Z","msg":"喂呀～"},{"pid":"c8bd38ad37aa8775d5b8e2c66db3b6dc0cdcb5f5","tid":695681,"uid":121473,"like":12,"dislike":39,"score":-27,"quote":{"pid":"fa82f30975d271bfa818b0dc56d3e77b83090af2","tid":695681,"uid":78622,"like":78,"dislike":64,"score":14,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-06-09T11:51:27.000Z","msg":"喂呀～"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-09T11:55:58.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" cla